##  Example AO Questions (Hands-On)

If I were the AO reviewing OpenMRS-on-AWS, hereâ€™s a question Iâ€™d ask:

> â€œCan you confirm that all third-party libraries in the OpenMRS deployment are monitored for vulnerabilities and patched in a timely manner?â€

This reflects real-world risk: third-party dependencies often introduce risk if left unmonitored.

